	   <tr><td colspan=1 id=headerrow>Posted @ Fri, Sep 22nd 3:02 PM 2000</td>
	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Good<span id=notbold>[4.00]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>As many of you have noticed the Dojo has left us.  The Sensei closed the site after deciding that he really didn't have the heart to carry on.  He gave us a lot; a place to grow our community.  He had all but quit EQ, so it was just natural progression that the Dojo would close its doors.<br><br>The message base is still available for reading, it is presently locked but does have a good bye post.  (<a href="http://pub.ezboard.com/bthedojo" target=_new>http://pub.ezboard.com/bthedojo</a>)<br><br>The nice thing though is that the monks have rallied behind Zadkiel from Xegony who has put up a new site called Monkly Business (www.monkly-business.com).<br><br>The new site features many of the same things that the Dojo offered, minus the Sensei's acerbic wit (I will miss it).  Forums just went live recently, and the quest, zone guides, and other valuable information for monks is swiftly filling up.  Stop by.<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
