	   <tr><td colspan=2>What happened to The Dojo?<br><br>No serious, the Dojo was the very BEST site for monks everywhere, and for the last few weeks, I couldn't get in to the friggin' site. I blame it on my computer being faulty, but lo and behold, they removed the Dojo site from the Allakhazam site list! No kidding, look for yourself, they took off the site!<br><br>What, did the people there ran out of humour sites? I was following their word like GOSPEL ever since I created my monk; the only other independent Monk site is relentless monks: they haven't updated their page since February!<br><br>Fellow Monk-eys, this is bad, real bad. I never highlighted their site address, depending on the Allakhazam link to get to the Dojo; now I'm stuck, slapping my head Homer Simpson-like while going "D'oh-jo!".<br><br>Any news and info would be appreciated. Because if Dojo doesn't come back, someone will actually need to form *gasp* another independant monk page! YIKES!<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
