	   <tr><td colspan=1 id=headerrow>Posted @ Tue, Oct 17th 11:00 PM 2000</td>
	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Excellent<span id=notbold>[5.00]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>I believe part of the problem is two or more light sources cancel each other out.  Case in point:  my troll has natural nightsight, and it's enhanced when I wear my split paw mask.  However, it loses it's enhancement when I pick up a lightstone and is in a general inventory slot.  Drop/sell one or place it inside a bag.  I suspect this will fix your nightsight problem.  Include with that those suggestions from others about adjusting your monitor and you will see fine in low light conditions.<br>Good luck young human nightblind monkey!<br>:D<br>&nbsp;<br>Emperor and Shamanic High Priest of the Trolls<br>"Worship Innoruuk, you worthless cattle!"<br></td></tr>
