	   <tr><td colspan=2>Just a thought that it might be a video card problem.  I played one machine using same character, a halfing druid and couldn't see squat, while perfectly fine on the other machine, difference being the video card.  Question is do you have one of those cheap ATI compaq video cards, if so get another card.  Humans can see perfectly fine at night with a GLS or even fire beetle eye with a decent video card, while a race that can see at night with SBS can't see in front of their face, because of the video card.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
