	   <tr><td colspan=2> This worked for me, but others say it does little or nothing: Go to the options screen in game, choose display. Now see that slider bar near the top of the screen *I know, I know, I should remember the name of it but I can't*? Move it to the right. Just a few clicks at a time. For me it made everything a bit brighter and at night I have very little problems seeing. In the day it can get too bright if you moved it too far, so either turn it back down or just don't move it too far in the first place :)<br> Also, follow SunZin's suggestions above, which are all good, and remember that enchanters aren't the only ones with such spells. I know shamans have a similar spell too. Maybe someone else could post if any other classes have spells for increased nightvision? <br> Last option, if nothing else works: Go to the nearest inn and drink 'til morning. Good luck!<br>&nbsp;<br>Beleni<br>Lowly Monk on Karana</td></tr>
