<table  border=0 cellpadding=2 cellspacing=0 awidth=100%><a name=9689572694679></a><form action=http://eqdb.allakhazam.com/strategy/mrate.pl name=f9689572694679><tr><td id=headerrow><a id=sj href=classes.html?class=3&mid=9689572694679>RE: First Magical Weapon</a> <a id=fs8 href=classes.html?class=3&mid=9689572694679#post><img src=http://everquest.allakhazam.com/static/reply.gif border=0 alt="Reply..." height=16 width=16></a></td><td align=right id=headerrow valign=bottom><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=96><span id= >xyleen</span></a>, <span id= > </span><br><span id=notbold>12 posts</td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 id=headerrow>Posted @ Thu, Sep 14th 2:47 PM 2000</td>
	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Good<span id=notbold>[4.00]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>Netted gloves from frogluks will work fine..in fact any glove that has the tag MAGIC will imbue your hand to hand fighting with the ability to land magical blows on the usually invulnerable creatures like ghouls and wisps.<br><br>As far as good blunt weapons, i believe any weapon with better stats per leven than the monks hand to hand will suffice.  Make sure you get two of them for greater damage output, although if you are lacking, you can wield a 1HB in your primary, your secondary is your other hand, which will still attack based on the dual wield percentage of your skill level with the damage/delay for hand to hand.<br>You could also place the 1HB in the secondary hand, and have the hand to hand as your primary.  Either way, whatever is in the secondary slot will hit less frequently.  <br>For 2HB i would say take a weapon with greater damage double or better the damage of your damage per level of fist with a decent delay. Try comparing the ratios of the hth to a 2hb weapon and see which has the higher damage output per unit second<br>Here is the dam/delay per level of a monks fists from the eqvault monk guide: <a href="http://eqvault.ign.com/guidebook/playerguides/monk/monk.shtml" target=_new>http://eqvault.ign.com/guidebook/playerguides/monk/monk.shtml</a><br><br>1 (4/36)<br>5 (5/36)<br>10 (6/36)<br>15 (7/36)<br>20 (8/36)<br>25 (9/35)<br>30 (10/34)<br>35 (11/33)<br>40 (12/32)<br>45 (13/31)<br>50 (14/30)<br>60 (14/26) <br>&nbsp;<br>20th Level Inky Shadowknight on Cazic-Thule server.</td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 >&nbsp;</td><td align=right valign=bottom>
